---
title: Pork Schnitzels & Dill-Parsley Mayo with Garlic Veggies & Herby Potato Mash
description: Here's a neat trick: when you're crumbing food, use one hand for the wet ingredients and the other for the dry so you don't end up with fingers that look like dagwood dogs! Give it a try when you make these golden pork schnitzels.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-schnitzel-creamy-parsley-mash-c8aa2930.jpg
